HEADWORD: Asserter
<hw>As*sert"er</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who asserts;
one who avers pr maintains; an assertor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The inflexible <qex>asserter</qex> of the rights of the
church.</q> <rj><qau>Milman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>asserting</ent>⟦br⟧
